|text1     = As the Store Level increases, the chance of characters with various costs appearing changes.<br />The higher the Store Level, the easier it is for higher-cost characters (4/5 cost) to appear.<br />The higher the Store Level, the harder it is for lower-cost characters (1/2/3 cost) to appear.
|image2    = Tutorial Ascension Tips How to Locate Character 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_10006302.png>-<Tutorial Ascension Tips How to Locate Character 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = How to find a desired character: Based on the target character's cost, refresh the Store at the level where the chance for the character to appear is highest.<br />For example: If your lineup has a 2-cost character as the main DPS stay at level 6 and refresh the store, where there is a 40% chance of encountering 2-cost characters.<br />Another example: For a lineup with a 4-cost character as the main DPS, reach Level 8 as soon as possible before refreshing the store to find that character.
